[2026-05-02 09:41:26.24603] [526998] [debug] Token: Crypt::PasswdMD5. Extras:
[2026-05-02 09:41:26.24606] [526998] [debug] 	- Crypt::PasswdMD5 in the random_md5_salt function uses the built-in rand function to generate a salt
[2026-05-02 09:41:26.24608] [526998] [debug] 	- The built-in rand function is not appropriate for cryptographic use, as it is predictable and seeded by only 32 bits
[2026-05-02 09:41:26.24610] [526998] [debug] 	- Use Crypt::SysRandom or Crypt::URandom to generate random bytes instead of calling rand
[2026-05-02 09:41:26.24612] [526998] [debug] 	- Or use Crypt::URandom::Token to generate the salt directly without having to convert the bytes into base-64 characters
